<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    We discussed this in book club! If you look at the prologue, Ava signs her introduction, dated March 2014. We decided that she is an old woman recount<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    We discussed this in book club! If you look at the prologue, Ava signs her introduction, dated March 2014. We decided that she is an old woman recounting the story, so she didn't die. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
